title: SPY + RAY BARBEE: Explorations in Sound and Music
description: Accompany SPY's Ray Barbee on a journey to a suspicious looking dome in the desert: a 38-foot high, 50-foot diameter all-wood structure designed to reflect and focus a range of frequencies useful for the rejuvenation of human beings.
